    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>夜市模拟器 – 演示版本</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本演示提供了《夜市模拟器》的早期预览。在演示版中，玩家可以建立一个基础的小店，销售有限的商品，并体验初步的顾客互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>演示版包含的内容：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开设一个小型商店，在有限空间内经营</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/97d67044aea265e3069523eeed8fabc3.poster.avif?t=1744422665\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/97d67044aea265e3069523eeed8fabc3.webm?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/97d67044aea265e3069523eeed8fabc3.mp4?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >销售特定类别中有限的商品（如食品饮料、清洁用品等）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/0517e3aefc5e236ebfc4b6d3331394f8.poster.avif?t=1744422665\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/0517e3aefc5e236ebfc4b6d3331394f8.webm?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/0517e3aefc5e236ebfc4b6d3331394f8.mp4?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用部分货架和设备选项布置商店</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/591ea0cdd08d4dd7c57eeb64f38acd5c.poster.avif?t=1744422665\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/591ea0cdd08d4dd7c57eeb64f38acd5c.webm?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/591ea0cdd08d4dd7c57eeb64f38acd5c.mp4?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验昼夜循环系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与顾客进行基础互动和交易</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/0e45d4087e39c1f6722ff8572b1def92.poster.avif?t=1744422665\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/0e45d4087e39c1f6722ff8572b1def92.webm?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/0e45d4087e39c1f6722ff8572b1def92.mp4?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基本支付系统（现金/刷卡）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/3e3cf5fc2a57e389d0cd8dc6afc7d950.poster.avif?t=1744422665\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/3e3cf5fc2a57e389d0cd8dc6afc7d950.webm?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233420/extras/3e3cf5fc2a57e389d0cd8dc6afc7d950.mp4?t=1744422665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过日终报告查看销售情况</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >演示版本内容有限，让玩家可以体验游戏的核心玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整版将包含更多功能、商品、商店扩展选项和更复杂的系统，但此演示仅限于